    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/814be9dc82ae6777364e02df1483a111.poster.avif?t=1753389587\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/814be9dc82ae6777364e02df1483a111.webm?t=1753389587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/814be9dc82ae6777364e02df1483a111.mp4?t=1753389587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/4a8c3c396ae89b82a39b0195e0b7c2a9.poster.avif?t=1753389587\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/4a8c3c396ae89b82a39b0195e0b7c2a9.webm?t=1753389587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/4a8c3c396ae89b82a39b0195e0b7c2a9.mp4?t=1753389587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world on the brink of destruction, one unlikely hero steps forward. KIDD, a young martial artist as swift with punches and kicks as he is with delivering your pizza, is humanity’s last hope. <i>Pizza Kidd</i> pulses with the spirit and edginess of 90s anime and the grit of classic arcade brawlers of the same era, blending beautifully detailed 16-bit pixel art with fast-paced, responsive combat. This isn’t just another &quot;indie&quot; game—it’s an electrifying homage to a golden era, crafted with love and modern flair to keep things feeling fresh yet familiar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/eeca12a976a72bede2792896f464ac0c.webp?t=1753389587\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Santos, the sinister architect behind the city's destruction, now commands an army of nightmares: creepy creature clones, zombified scarecrow ninjas that strike without warning, drone bots that patrol the gates, and towering monstrous behemoths that crush everything in their path. The streets are crawling with terror, but KIDD’s mission is clear—recover the 8 sacred seed stones, harness their power, and put an end to Santos' reign of madness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/b3102a697464aa62419e75326008640f.poster.avif?t=1753389587\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/b3102a697464aa62419e75326008640f.webm?t=1753389587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/b3102a697464aa62419e75326008640f.mp4?t=1753389587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/1d9a86d2217ba391e2de5d504869155f.webp?t=1753389587\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><br>Unleash the Action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>High-Impact Combat</strong>: Fast, responsive attacks, air juggling, and long chain combos for intense gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Side-Scrolling Adventure</strong>: Expansive 2D levels with skill-based, fighting-style special moves.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Retro Pixel Brilliance</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Vivid 16-Bit Art</strong>: Hand-drawn, comic-style pixel art with detailed stages, big character sprites, and explosive effects.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Sound that Hits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Arcade Crunch Sound Design</strong>: Satisfying impact with every hit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Epic Soundtrack by Kevin Ripley</strong>: Original music that amplifies the energy and action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/321ee1837572f3d66924692ef8194605.webp?t=1753389587\" width=612 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/c8c3797d2b7f4883d8c02327a07f4afd.poster.avif?t=1753389587\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/c8c3797d2b7f4883d8c02327a07f4afd.webm?t=1753389587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/c8c3797d2b7f4883d8c02327a07f4afd.mp4?t=1753389587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>*Please note:<strong> The Pizza Kidd Steam demo is still in active development.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142990/extras/71c4300462da4b10f4ba9cb267fb221e.avif?t=1753389587\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>#PIZZAKIDD</strong></i></p>",
